’Ł@0941922ee05f30c06b7d26774a3a8187f24371350c0514d4e7c9993b3d9f6a8bŁīTitle: title: do
Path: Flags
Content:
``--ignore-errors, -i``
: Ignore errors as the closure runs.
``--capture-errors, -c``
: Catch errors as the closure runs, and return them.
``--env``
: Keep the environment defined inside the command.
’Ł@2db3b8f71cb6afeb09bb3b5a59d856275c2ef998792120b746844431c7811cd4Ł}Title: title: do
Path: Parameters
Content:
``closure``
: The closure to run.
``...rest``
: The parameter(s) for the closure.
